%2Cimgsize-34686.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup%2Ffact-check-did-match-referee-andy-pycroft-apologise-to-pakistan-cricket-team%2Farticleshow%2F123966858.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20threatened%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20after%20a%20perceived%20slight%20during%20the%20India-Pakistan%20match%2C%20claiming%20that%20India%20captain%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20refused%20to%20shake%20hands%20with%20Pakistani%20counterpart%20Salman%20Ali%20Agha.%20The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20said%20match%20referee%20Andy%20Pycroft%20apologised%20for%20miscommunication.%20But%20did%20he%3F%20We%20fact%20check%20that%20claim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20real%20force%20powering%20China's%20market%20rally%20isn't%20mom-and-pop%20investors%20this%20time%2C%20says%20Goldman%20Sachs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226597%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Investors%20monitor%20share%20prices%20at%20a%20securities%20trading%20office%20in%20Shanghai%2C%20China.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cb762957d362d375e8629a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224398%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInvestors%20monitor%20share%20prices%20at%20a%20securities%20trading%20office%20in%20Shanghai%2C%20China.%3Cp%3EVCG%2FVCG%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInstitutional%20investors%20%E2%80%94%20not%20retail%20traders%20%E2%80%94%20are%20powering%20China's%20stock%20rally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20rally%20may%20have%20room%20to%20run%20as%20households%20hold%20only%20a%20small%20slice%20of%20wealth%20in%20stocks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20is%20sticking%20with%20its%20overweight%20call%20on%20Chinese%20stocks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fchina%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina's%20stock%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20on%20a%20hot%20rally%20after%20years%20of%20gloom%2C%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%20says%20the%20bull%20run%20may%20have%20further%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%2C%20contrary%20to%20popular%20narrative%2C%20China's%20millions%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Finvesting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emom-and-pop%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20the%20ones%20powering%20the%20surge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20show%20that%20institutional%20investors%20have%20actually%20provided%20much%20of%20the%20capital%2C%20wrote%20analysts%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20in%20a%20Thursday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20equities%20have%20added%20about%20%243%20trillion%20in%20market%20value%20this%20year%20across%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20mainland%20markets%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs.%20The%20CSI%20300%20index%20of%20large%20mainland%20companies%20has%20jumped%2026%25%20since%20April%2C%20and%20the%20MSCI%20China%20index%20alone%20has%20climbed%20over%2035%25%20year-to-date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surge%20comes%20on%20the%20back%20of%20heavy%20institutional%20buying%2C%20including%20onshore%20mutual%20funds%20that%20have%20slashed%20cash%20ratios%20to%20five-year%20lows%20as%20they%20rushed%20into%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20domestic%20insurers%20lifted%20their%20equity%20holdings%20by%2026%25%2C%20while%20domestic%20hedge%20funds%20have%20grown%20assets%20under%20management%20from%205%20trillion%20Chinese%20yuan%20in%20September%202024%20to%205.9%20trillion%20yuan%2C%20or%20%24830%20billion%2C%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForeign%20investors%20have%20also%20piled%20in.%20Goldman's%20data%20showed%20its%20global%20hedge%20fund%20clients%20made%20their%20biggest%20one-month%20move%20into%20mainland%20China's%20A-shares%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20households%20hold%20about%20%245%20trillion%20in%20equities%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20a%20third%20of%20the%20total%20Chinese%20equities%20market%20%E2%80%94%20while%20most%20of%20the%20rest%20is%20dominated%20by%20global%20and%20domestic%20institutional%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248410c08-32c5-435c-bdc4-3a04493d0018%5C%22%3EOnly%20a%20small%20slice%20of%20household%20wealth%20is%20in%20stocks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20analysts%20say%20they%20expect%20Chinese%20households%20to%20gradually%20put%20more%20money%20into%20stocks%2C%20since%20they%20remain%20underweight%20compared%20to%20global%20peers.%20Just%2011%25%20of%20Chinese%20household%20financial%20assets%20are%20in%20equities%20or%20mutual%20funds%2C%20versus%20about%2032%25%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20property%20prices%20down%20sharply%20from%20their%20peak%20and%20bank%20deposits%20yielding%20under%202%25%2C%20families%20may%20slowly%20redirect%20more%20wealth%20into%20equities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20sentiment%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20still%20%26quot%3Bnowhere%20near%20the%20euphoric%20levels%20in%20mid-2015%20or%20late%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Goldman.%20If%20enthusiasm%20returned%20to%20those%20highs%2C%20the%20CSI%20300%20could%20gain%20another%2018%25%20to%2027%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20report%20came%20amid%20concerns%20about%20the%20market%20overheating%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Chinese%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-nvidia-ai-chip-ban-china-chip-tech-stock-overheating-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20stock%20rally%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20was%20first%20sparked%20by%20the%20breakout%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-praises-deepseek-gift-world-ai-industry-inference-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAI%20model%20DeepSeek%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0early%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20analysts%20wrote%20that%20valuations%20don't%20look%20stretched%20and%20Chinese%20shares%20still%20trade%20at%20a%20discount%20to%20developed-market%20equities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina's%20stock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20outpaced%20its%20slowing%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20with%20retail%20sales%20and%20industrial%20production%20recently%20missing%20forecasts%20%E2%80%94%20Goldman%20notes%20this%20gap%20between%20financial%20markets%20and%20the%20real%20economy%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20global%20phenomenon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20risk%20is%20policy%2C%20Goldman's%20analysts%20wrote.%20Previous%20market%20rallies%20ended%20when%20regulators%20tightened%20leverage%20or%20cracked%20down%20on%20private%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20stock%20market%20has%20become%20too%20important%20for%20Beijing%20to%20deliberately%20knock%20down%2C%20because%20it%20helps%20fund%20new%20technology%2C%20channel%20capital%20to%20productive%20sectors%2C%20and%20build%20household%20wealth%20and%20sentiment%2C%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20policy-engineered%20equity%20downturn%20is%20low%20unless%20there%20is%20clearer%20evidence%20of%20valuation%20excess%20and%20rampant%20speculation%20emerges%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20is%20maintaining%20its%20overweight%20call%20on%20China's%20mainland-listed%20A%20shares%20and%20Hong%20Kong-listed%20H%20shares%2C%20forecasting%208%25%20and%203%25%20upside%20over%20the%20next%2012%20months%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-stock-market-rally-forecast-institutional-investors-not-retail-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758178725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cb765957d362d375e8629c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsid