le.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20pitched%20AI-powered%20wearables%20as%20the%20next%20must-have%20item%20at%20Wednesday's%20annual%20Meta%20Connect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGlasses%20are%20the%20ideal%20form%20factor%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzuckerberg-meta-ai-glasses-cognitive-disadvantage-q2-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20super%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they%20let%20you%20stay%20present%20in%20the%20moment%20while%20getting%20access%20to%20all%20of%20these%20AI%20capabilities%20to%20make%20you%20smarter%2C%20help%20you%20communicate%20better%2C%20improve%20your%20memory%2C%20improve%20your%20senses%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zuckerberg%20as%20he%20took%20the%20stage%20in%20Menlo%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcements%20confirmed%20a%20leaked%20video%20from%20Meta%20on%20Monday%2C%20which%20teased%20a%20neural%20wristband%20for%20the%20Ray-Ban%20Meta%20glasses%20and%20a%20sport-focused%20model%20of%20the%20Oakley%20Vanguard%20smart%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20shares%20gained%20moderately%20in%20after-hours%20trading%2C%20up%20half%20a%20percentage%20point%20at%20the%20close%20of%20Zuckerberg's%20keynote%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20four%20biggest%20product%20announcements%20out%20of%20Meta%20Connect%2C%20plus%20a%20big%20tech%20snafu%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ffd3919d-2596-4f9b-b4c9-4e51c5495b62%5C%22%3E1.%20A%20stepping%20stone%20to%20Orion%20glasses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20relatively%20affordable%20Ray-Ban%20Meta%20glasses%2C%20which%20start%20at%20%24299%20and%20have%20already%20sold%20over%202%20million%20units%2C%20will%20be%20upgraded%20with%20a%20new%20display%20and%20a%20neural%20wristband%20with%20surface%20electromyography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20display%20glasses%20will%20include%20a%20full-color%20in-lens%20display%20for%20tasks%20like%20messages%2C%20photos%2C%20and%20Meta%20AI%20prompts%2C%20with%20built-in%20cameras%20and%20audio%20and%20up%20to%20six%20hours%20of%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20original%2C%20iconic%20designs.%20I%20think%20these%20are%20the%20most%20popular%20glasses%20design%20in%20history%2C%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Zuckerberg%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Ray-Ban%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wear%20them%20all%20day%2C%20they%20never%20run%20out%20of%20battery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20glasses%2C%20developed%20in%20partnership%20with%20EssilorLuxottica%2C%20will%20launch%20in%20two%20frame%20sizes%20and%20colors%20starting%20September%2030%20at%20select%20US%20retailers%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-buy-trained-30k-employees-to-help-sell-ai-computers-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBest%20Buy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20LensCrafters%2C%20and%20Ray-Ban%20stores%2C%20with%20a%20price%20tag%20of%20%24799%20for%20the%20set.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20could%20see%20a%20gradual%20rollout%20by%20early%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pricing%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20gradual%20ascent%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forion-meta-ar-smart-glasses-review-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOrion%20AI%20glasses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20not%20publicly%20available.%20Zuckerberg%20previously%20said%20the%20augmented%20reality-focused%20Orion%20would%20cost%20%2410%2C000%20to%20make%20per%20pair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214d406be-a7fd-4087-8ffd-cd73a3573e6d%5C%22%3E2.%20The%20neural%20wristband%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20glasses'%20complementary%20wristband%20can%20detect%20muscle%20motions%20and%20may%20be%20able%20to%20detect%20subtle%20finger%20movements%20that%20would%20allow%20you%20to%20type%20and%20control%20your%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20called%20the%20neural%20band%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20scientific%20breakthrough%26quot%3B%20and%20added%20that%20it%20is%20available%20in%20various%20colors%2C%20is%20water-resistant%2C%20and%20has%20an%2018-hour%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20live%20demo%2C%20Zuckerberg%20showed%20audiences%20how%20he%20used%20the%20wristband%20to%20type%20and%20send%20WhatsApp%20messages%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-andrew-bosworth-predictions-ai-impact-on-software-engineering-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta's%20chief%20tech%20officer%2C%20Andrew%20Bosworth%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad0da36e-36fb-4119-bcd0-88c8e1fd32b6%5C%22%3E3.%20'Era%20of%20athletic%20intelligence'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20be%20in%20luck%20if%20you're%20both%20a%20fan%20of%20tech%20and%20high-intensity%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20unveiled%20a%20new%20line%20of%20performance-focused%20AI%20glasses%20designed%20in%20partnership%20with%20Oakley.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20new%20product%2C%20named%20Vanguard%2C%20is%20available%20for%20pre-order%20ahead%20of%20its%20October%2021%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20taken%20them%20out%20surfing%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20said%20the%20Vangaurd%20would%20adopt%20Oakley's%20wraparound%20design%2C%20with%20a%20lens%20that%20blocks%20out%20dust%20and%20sun%2C%20alongside%20the%20most%20water-resistant%20frame%20among%20all%20Meta%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Meta%2C%20an%20athlete%20who%20has%20a%20Vanguard%20and%20a%20compatible%20Garmin-branded%20device%20could%20ask%20its%20AI%20system%20what%20their%20heart%3Cs%3E%20%3C%2Fs%3Erate%20or%20speed%20is%20and%20use%20voice%20commands%20to%20get%20feedback%20on%20their%20performance.%20The%20glasses%20allow%20users%20to%20capture%20video%20hands-free%20in%20up%20to%203K%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246629f5d-ac0a-4acf-9a46-01f540307c19%5C%22%3E4.%20Meta's%20new%20VR%20feature%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Connect%2C%20Zuckerberg%20unveiled%20an%20upgrade%20that%20allows%20users%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fmeta-quest-3s-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EQuest%20headset%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20scan%20a%20room%20in%20a%20few%20minutes%20and%20explore%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scan%20creates%20what%20Zuckerberg%20called%20%26quot%3Bimmersive%2C%20true-to-life%20virtual%20experiences%26quot%3B%20with%20realistic%20physics%20and%20interactions.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20pretty%20awesome%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%2C%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-connect-live-updates-mark-zuckerberg-keynote-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20is%20available%20to%20developers%20and%20creators.%20It's%20part%20of%20Meta's%20long-running%20plan%20to%20build%20realistic%20digital%20worlds%20%E2%80%94%20what%20it%20calls%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-metaverse-reality-labs-legendary-misadventure-memo-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMetaverse%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20that%20people%20live%20and%20interact%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244a6330f-dd00-4ebb-ac28-99854c2ee046%5C%22%3E5.%20Live%20demo%20glitches%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20big%20unveiling%20of%20its%20next%20wave%20of%20AI-powered%20glasses%20was%20overshadowed%20by%20awkward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzuckerbergs-meta-ai-glasses-demo-goes-wrong-live-stage-twice-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20demo%20failures%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Zuckerberg%20introduced%20the%20second-generation%20Ray-Ban%20Meta%20glasses%20and%20projected%20chef%20Jack%20Mancuso%20on%20the%20big%20screen%20to%20showcase%20the%20glasses%20in%20action%2C%20things%20went%20sideways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20skipped%20steps%2C%20ignored%20follow-up%20questions%2C%20and%20repeated%20itself%20when%20asked%20to%20provide%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20make%20a%20Korean-inspired%20steak%20sauce.%20Mancuso%20blamed%20it%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bmessed%20up%26quot%3B%20WiFi%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20setbacks%20continued%20when%20Zuckerberg%20attempted%20to%20demo%20the%20neural%20wristband.%20After%20typing%20a%20message%20to%20Bosworth%2C%20Zuckerberg%20tried%20to%20answer%20a%20live%20video%20call%2C%20only%20to%20fail%20multiple%20times%20as%20the%20wristband%20didn't%20respond.%20Bosworth%20eventually%20joined%20him%20onstage%20to%20say%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BWiFi%20is%20brutal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20practice%20these%20things%20like%20100%20times%2C%20and%20then%20you%20never%20know%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246629f5d-ac0a-4acf-9a46-01f540307c19%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-biggest-takeaways-mark-zuckerberg-meta-connect-ai-glasses-products-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758171777000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cb6087183847aa39d6fd87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-biggest-takeaways-mark-zuckerberg-meta-connect-ai-glasses-products-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mark%20Zuckerberg%20announced%20a%20slate%20of%20products%20in%20his%20big%20reveal%20of%20what's%20next%20for%20Meta.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li%2CCharles%20Rollet%2CShubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A71%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-biggest-takeaways-mark-zuckerberg-meta-connect-ai-glasses-products-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22