%20a%20hit%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20its%20rollout%20and%20subsequent%20rollback%20of%20its%20updated%20logo%2C%20but%20its%20core%20audience%20of%20diners%20aged%2065%20and%20up%20has%20seen%20less%20severe%20declines%20than%20other%20demographics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESign-ups%20for%20its%20loyalty%20program%20were%20also%20up.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20CEO%20%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22unset%5C%22%3EJulie%20Felss%20Masino%3C%2Fmark%3E%20said%20Cracker%20Barrel%20saw%20its%20rewards%20program%20membership%20increase%20by%203%20million%20people%2C%20with%20a%20spike%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20despite%20the%20rebranding%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraffic%20is%20down%20since%208%2F19%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-courts-gen-z-new-dorm-room-merchandise-loyalty-program-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eloyalty%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20sign-ups%20are%20actually%20ahead%20of%20our%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20Masino%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20August%2019th%2C%20when%20the%20new%20logo%20was%20first%20unveiled.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we've%20signed%20up%20about%20400%2C000%20people%20quarter%20to%20date%2C%20and%20300%2C000%20of%20those%20people%20have%20come%20in%20since%208%2F19%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0again%2C%20exceeding%20our%20plan%2C%20exceeding%20our%20expectations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20than%209%20million%20total%20registered%20members%20of%20Cracker%20Barrel's%20loyalty%20program%20account%20for%20over%2035%25%20of%20tracked%20sales%20and%20an%20even%20higher%20percentage%20of%20retail%20sales%2C%20Masino%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCracker%20Barrel%20definitely%20still%20has%20a%20customer%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeremy%20Bowman%2C%20an%20analyst%20covering%20consumer%20goods%20for%20The%20Motley%20Fool%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%2C%20often%2C%20the%20way%20stories%20like%20this%20get%20portrayed%20among%20investors%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20the%20media%20is%20that%20they're%20doing%20terribly.%20But%20it's%20not%20exactly%20a%20crisis%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20they%20are%20still%20certainly%20profitable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETruist%20analyst%20Jake%20Bartlett%20wrote%20in%20a%20research%20note%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bbuy%26quot%3B%20rating%20published%20Wednesday%20evening%20following%20the%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20core%20drivers%20of%20Cracker%20Barrel's%20brand%20turnaround%2C%20including%20improved%20menu%20innovation%20and%20service%2C%20remain%20intact%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bsales%20may%20start%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20re-branding%20backlash%20soon%20with%20the%20resumption%20of%20the%20Fall%20Menu%20marketing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBowman%20added%20that%20Cracker%20Barrel's%20unique%20business%20model%2C%20which%20combines%20its%20southern%20restaurants%20with%20retail%20shops%2C%20offers%20dual%20revenue%20streams%20that%20appeal%20to%20customers%20and%20investors%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20from%20InMarket%20found%20that%20Cracker%20Barrel%20had%20the%20second-most%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcracker-barrel-customers-divided-renovations-menu-refresh-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloyal%20fans%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20casual%20restaurant%20sector%20in%20Q2.%20This%20rating%20was%20based%20on%20the%20chain's%20%26quot%3Bfidelity%20index%26quot%3B%20of%20174%2C%20a%20score%20determined%20by%20the%20ratio%20of%20guest%20visits%20to%20a%20location%20compared%20to%20the%20chain's%20nationwide%20number%20of%20locations.%20A%20score%20of%20100%20is%20considered%20%26quot%3Bon%20par%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20visits%20and%20locations%20per%20chain%2C%20with%20a%20score%20greater%20than%20100%20indicating%20the%20chain%20is%20%26quot%3Bexcelling%20at%20attracting%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20see%20how%20that%20loyalty%20continues%20to%20sort%20of%20deliver%20a%20win%20for%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Bowman%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%2C%20over%20the%20long%20term%2C%20they%20still%20need%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20bring%20in%20that%20next%20generation%20of%20family%20customers.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20you%20want%20to%20rely%20too%20much%20on%20the%20over-65%20demographic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Cracker%20Barrel%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcracker-barrel-q4-earnings-stock-loyal-fans-foot-traffic-sales-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758167209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cb4f3b183847aa39d6fcc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcracker-barrel-q4-earnings-stock-loyal-fans-foot-traffic-sales-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20though%20its%20Q4%20report%20saw%20Cracker%20Barrel's%20stock%20slide%20nearly%2010%25%2C%20a%20closer%20read%20of%20its%20earnings%20call%20shows%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%3A%20its%20superfans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcracker-barrel-q4-earnings-stock-loyal-fans-foot-traffic-sales-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alexei%20Navalny's%20widow%20says%20lab%20reports%20show%20her%20husband%20was%20poisoned%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758166942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123962695%2Cimgsize-650494.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Falexei-navalnys-widow-says-lab-reports-show-her-husband-was-poisoned%2Farticleshow%2F123962643.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A